Test whether object is an AD2CP type

Source: R/adp.nortek.ad2cp.R
is.ad2cp.Rd

Test whether object is an AD2CP type

is.ad2cp(x)

Arguments

x

an oce object.

Value

Logical value indicating whether x is an adp object, with fileType in its metadata slot equal to "AD2CP".
